    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 1.4,
      "top_in": 2.5598064304461943,
      "width_in": 10.83,
      "height_in": 0.7575,
      "text": "Waiting for the brilliant idea.  Google was the 20th search engine. Facebook was the 20th social network. A good enough idea plus great execution wins.",
      "font_size_pt": 21.0,
      "font_bold": true,
      "font_italic": false,
      "font_name": "SF Pro Display",
      "color": "090B11",
      "fill": null,
      "alignment": "left",
      "z": 4
    },
    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 1.4,
      "top_in": 3.5573053368328957,
      "width_in": 10.83,
      "height_in": 0.7575,
      "text": "Jumping into the first idea.  Spend at least two weeks deciding what to work on, not two minutes. You will spend years on this.",
      "font_size_pt": 21.0,
      "font_bold": true,
      "font_italic": false,
      "font_name": "SF Pro Display",
      "color": "090B11",
      "fill": null,
      "alignment": "left",
      "z": 6
    },
    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 1.4,
      "top_in": 4.554806430446194,
      "width_in": 10.83,
      "height_in": 0.7575,
      "text": "Starting with a solution, not a problem.  \u2018Uber for plumbers\u2019 is a solution looking for a problem. Always begin with a real, painful problem.",
      "font_size_pt": 21.0,
      "font_bold": true,
      "font_italic": false,
      "font_name": "SF Pro Display",
      "color": "090B11",
      "fill": null,
      "alignment": "left",
      "z": 8
    },
    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 1.4,
      "top_in": 5.552306430446194,
      "width_in": 10.83,
      "height_in": 0.7575,
      "text": "Believing ideas are hard to find.  Real problems are everywhere. Once you train your eye, ideas appear all around you.",
      "font_size_pt": 21.0,
      "font_bold": true,
      "font_italic": false,
      "font_name": "SF Pro Display",
      "color": "090B11",
      "fill": null,
      "alignment": "left",
      "z": 10
    },
    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 1.4,
      "top_in": 6.641792432195976,
      "width_in": 10.83,
      "height_in": 0.41666885389326336,
      "text": "Not pivoting when you need to.  Don\u2019t get in love with your idea. Get in love with the problem",
      "font_size_pt": 21.0,
      "font_bold": true,
      "font_italic": false,
      "font_name": "SF Pro Display",
      "color": "090B11",
